description: The first applicant almost made me doubt my judgment. From the moment he walked in the room I suspected him to be gay. He even used to work as an au pair. This will be easy, I thought. But he was totally shocked by my naughty offer. It took him a while to put himself together. He looked a bit shaken even as he was leaving. I just wanted to help him! The next guy was a typical example of a too cool to be here attitude of today’s youth. This smug and apathetic boy liked the job but was more than reluctant to pay the fee. He said he’s a hockey player which was enough for me to offer him my help. He agreed, in a very arrogant way. His cock was kind of disappointing at first but he proved to be a quite a grower.
title: Dirty Scout 05
